    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIR\nCALIFORNIA\nSystem Timetable\nEffective March 24, 1980\nNew Portland Service",
      "Now serving Portland!\nWe're growing to bring convenient,\neconomical air travel to more places in\nthe West.\nSo Air California is making it easy to\nfly between Portland and cities across\nCalifornia and Nevada. Our Sunjets\nare now linking Portland with San Jose,\nOakland, Reno, Orange County\nand Ontario.\nWe're Air California. We make it\neasy to fly."
